# LocalConvert Project Intelligence

## Project Overview
LocalConvert is a privacy-focused local file converter built with Tauri v2 + React.
All conversions happen locally using external tools (FFmpeg, ImageMagick, etc.).

## Key Patterns

### Frontend (React)
- Use Zustand for state management (store in `src/store/useStore.ts`)
- Use Framer Motion for animations (AnimatePresence for enter/exit)
- Use Tailwind CSS with custom colors defined in `tailwind.config.js`
- Components are in `src/components/`
- Format definitions in `src/types/formats.ts`

### Backend (Rust/Tauri)
- Commands defined in `src-tauri/src/commands.rs`
- Conversion logic in `src-tauri/src/converter.rs`
- Tool detection in `src-tauri/src/tools.rs`
- Types in `src-tauri/src/types.rs`

### Coding Standards
- TypeScript strict mode
- Async/await for all Tauri commands
- Motion components for interactive elements
- Toast notifications for user feedback

## Important Files
- `src/store/useStore.ts` - Central state management
- `src/types/formats.ts` - Format definitions and conversions
- `src-tauri/src/commands.rs` - Tauri command implementations
- `src-tauri/tauri.conf.json` - Tauri configuration

## Development Commands
```bash
npm run tauri dev    # Development mode
npm run tauri build  # Production build
```

## External Tool Dependencies
- FFmpeg (video/audio)
- ImageMagick (images)
- LibreOffice (documents)
- Pandoc (markdown/html)
- Ghostscript (PDF)
- Tesseract (OCR)
- 7-Zip (archives)

## UI Theme
- Dark mode by default
- Primary color: accent-600 (#4f46e5)
- Background: dark-900 (#0d0d0f) to dark-800 (#343541)
- Text: white/dark-300/dark-400

## User Preferences
- Always maintain privacy focus (no network for conversions)
- Keep UI minimal but powerful
- Provide feedback for all actions
- Support batch operations
